## Key CLI Commands

These are your primary tools. Use them from the `{{ project_name }}/` directory.

```bash
# Check your current status and active agent
agentic status

# Log a significant decision
agentic decision --title "Use microservices architecture" --rationale "Needed for scalability and team autonomy."

# Log a working assumption
agentic assumption --assumption "The external API will have a rate limit of 1000/min" --rationale "Standard for this type of service."

# Handoff to the next agent when your work is complete
agentic handoff --to <NEXT_AGENT_ID> --artifacts "file1.md,file2.md" --notes "Work completed and ready for next phase"
```

